descriptionHtml:
Download Invoice Labs <\b> Invoice Maker to create professional invoices, bills, quotes, and estimates in seconds. The app allows users to send invoices and estimates via text, email, and many other mediums. It also allows you to track the delivery, opening, and payment statuses.

The app allows you to focus on your core business, keeps you organized, and makes you look professional in front of your customer with very little time and effort

Why should you download this app?
The advanced user interface of the app allows you to generate high-quality invoices and estimates in less than a minute. All your invoices and estimates are saved on the cloud safely and securely so that you can access them at any time and can easily track the payment status. Managing your business with this app is easy and professional like never before.

User Friendly
The user interface and the user experience of the app have been designed in such a way that it provides maximum ease for the quick creation of professional invoices and estimates.
All your items, services, and clients can be saved for future use, ensuring that you never have to redo the hard work and are able to move more swiftly.

Professional Invoice template <\b>
The app provides you a beautiful and professional invoice template that you can customize using your logo, making you look highly professional.

Trackable invoice statuses<\b>
All the invoices are trackable and the app notifies you whenever the invoices are read. You can also track the payment status of the invoices.

Everything stored securely on cloud <\b>
Every invoice, estimate, client info is saved securely on the cloud automatically and is retrievable at any time. No need to worry if your phone is lost or stolen. All you need to do is to log in to your new phone and all your data will be available for your access.

Features<\b>

Invoice and Estimates<\b>
Create Invoices and estimates for any product, item, or service.
Customizable invoice and estimate numbers and titles.
Create an invoice from the estimate with a single button click.
Due dates for invoices.
Discount on item or total.
Description of the item.
Add signature to your invoices and estimates.
Add images and notes to invoices and estimates.
Save client information for future use.
Save items for future use.
Use customer’s info from phone contacts.
Customize business info and payment instructions for invoices and estimates.
Share (via email or pdf link)
Duplicate, edit, delete existing invoices and estimates.
Searching invoice and estimates via client name.
Add multiple payments in an invoice.
Mark invoice paid with a single click.
View email history and status of an invoice
Customize tax rate per item or mark individual items taxable/nontaxable in both invoices/estimates.
Get notified when your customer opens the invoice.

Settings<\b>
Save default payment instructions, email message, tax, and notes for automatic.
Customize currency and date formats.
Receive a copy of emails on business email.

Client<\b>
Add, edit view, search (via client name), delete client’s data.

Items<\b>
Add, edit view, search (via item title), delete item’s data.

Report<\b>
Reports provide you a complete picture of the invoices along with payment status

With the free version of the app, you can generate a limited number of invoices. To create unlimited invoices you have to upgrade.

For support, email support@invoicelabs.co<\b>

 Unlimited premium invoicing

Generating Invoices
• Generate invoices in less than a minute.

User-friendly Interface
• Easy and manageable invoice generator.

Estimate Management

Invoice Tracking and Email Acknowledgment
• Keep track of all the invoice s delivered

Work Globally
• Handle international clients professionally
• Offers extensive options for multiple currencies support

Storage
• Store data securely on the cloud
• Access previous logs from any device according to ease
• Save yourself from time-consuming bookkeeping
• Generate logging reports automatically
• Keep your invoice reports compact and manageable

• Generate free invoice s in the trial version
• Get access to unlimited invoice generation through premium membership

Why Invoicelabs?
